---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Nursing Scrubs Collections | Premium 205G / Standard 180G / Lightweight 130G | Yilong" 
  description="Professional nursing scrub sets in three fabric tiers: Premium 205 GSM (FIGs-quality), Standard 180 GSM (durable), Lightweight 130 GSM (breathable). OEKO-TEX certified. Low MOQ from 10 sets."
  keywords="nursing scrub sets, premium medical scrubs, wholesale scrubs, jogger scrub set, V-neck scrubs, 205 GSM scrubs, hospital uniform"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-center italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Nursing Scrub Collections</h1>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-500 mb-8 md:mb-12 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto italic">Engineered for the modern healthcare professional. Three fabric tiers for different markets and budgets.</p>
    
    <!-- ==================== FABRIC SELECTION GUIDE (NEW) ==================== -->
    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-12 border border-slate-200">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-2xl">🧵</span>
        <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Not sure which fabric to choose? Here's a quick guide:</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border-l-4 border-secondary">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Premium 205 GSM</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Building a US/Canada brand, want FIGs-quality feel? Ultra-soft, silky drape, 4-way stretch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Standard 180 GSM</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Hospital supply, wholesale, or uniform orders? Durable, comfortable, great value.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border-l-4 border-orange-400">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Lightweight 130 GSM</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Hot climate markets (Philippines, Africa, LATAM)? Lightweight, breathable, quick-dry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 text-center">All three tiers are OEKO-TEX® certified and available in XXS–6XL. <a href="/fabric-technology" class="text-secondary font-bold hover:underline">Learn more about our fabrics →</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Shop by Style -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400 mb-8 text-center italic">Shop by Style</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:gap-8 italic">
        <a href="#elite" class="px-6 py-2 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-black rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition">V-Neck Sets</a>
        <a href="#elite" class="px-6 py-2 border-2 border-secondary text-secondary font-black rounded-full hover:bg-secondary hover:text-white transition">Jogger Pants</a>
        <a href="#jumpsuit" class="px-6 py-2 border-2 border-indigo-600 text-indigo-600 font-black rounded-full hover:bg-indigo-600 hover:text-white transition">Jumpsuits</a>
        <a href="#bulk" class="px-6 py-2 border-2 border-slate-900 text-slate-900 font-black rounded-full hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition">Bulk Orders</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-20 md:space-y-32 text-left">
      <!-- Elite Series -->
      <div id="elite" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-600 font-bold rounded-full text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic text-red-600">Elite Series</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight text-red-900 underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">Premium V-Neck<br class="hidden md:block"/>Burgundy Scrub Set</h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic text-slate-600">The pinnacle of style and function. Featuring our most popular burgundy hue, this female-tailored set is designed for professionals who prioritize both performance and a modern silhouette.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl mb-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-widest mb-3 italic">Professional Fabric Specs</h4>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-red-600 italic">72% Polyester / 21% Rayon / 7% Spandex</p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2 italic text-slate-500">Weight: 205GSM | Style: Modern Tailored Fit | Features: 4-Way Stretch, Multi-Pocket Design</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-4 italic italic text-red-900">Available in: Burgundy, Navy, Charcoal, and Hunter Green.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] md:rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A5cf89e66f8724400a9dff9b9bac7cd03O.png" alt="Premium Burgundy Jogger Nursing Scrub Set" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 md:bottom-8 left-6 md:left-8 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-4 md:px-6 py-2 md:py-3 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl text-[10px] md:text-xs font-black uppercase italic text-red-600 shadow-lg border border-red-100">Burgundy Collection</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Versatile Series -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] md:rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A7e11502b0045464da109007ec18708f30.png" alt="Royal Blue Classic V-neck Scrub Set" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 md:bottom-8 right-6 md:right-8 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-4 md:px-6 py-2 md:py-3 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl text-[10px] md:text-xs font-black uppercase italic text-blue-600 shadow-lg border border-blue-100">Royal Blue Collection</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-left">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold rounded-full text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic text-primary">Versatile Series</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight text-primary underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">Classic Royal Blue<br class="hidden md:block"/>Modern Scrub Set</h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic text-slate-600">The industry gold standard for men. A timeless design combined with modern moisture-wicking technology for the everyday healthcare hero.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl mb-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-widest mb-3 italic">Professional Fabric Specs</h4>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-primary italic">Polyester / Spandex Performance Blend</p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2 italic text-slate-500">Weight: 180GSM | Style: Traditional V-Neck | Features: Easy Care, Wrinkle-Resistant</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-r-4 lg:border-r-0 lg:border-l-4 border-primary pr-4 lg:pr-0 lg:pl-4 italic text-primary">Best for: General Nursing, Dental Clinics, and Medical Teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- One-Piece Jumpsuit -->
      <div id="jumpsuit" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 font-bold rounded-full text-[10px] md:text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic text-indigo-600">Jumpsuit Series</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight text-indigo-900 underline decoration-2 underline-offset-8">Signature Charcoal Grey<br class="hidden md:block"/>Medical Scrub Jumpsuit</h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic text-slate-600">Elevate your professional wardrobe with our signature one-piece jumpsuit. Combining high-end professional elegance with hospital-grade durability.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl mb-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-400 tracking-widest mb-3 italic">Professional Fabric Specs</h4>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-indigo-600 italic">Signature Poly-Flex Rayon Blend</p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2 italic text-slate-500">Weight: 195GSM | Style: Cinched Waist Jumpsuit | Features: Concealed Zip, Multiple Pockets</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 border-l-4 border-indigo-600 pl-4 italic text-indigo-900">Ideal for: Aesthetic Clinics, Pediatrics, and Specialized Spas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] md:rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/Afa9b2c28a97f47c5892c840728a7e217Y.png" alt="Charcoal Grey One-Piece Medical Scrub Jumpsuit" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 md:bottom-8 left-6 md:left-8 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-4 md:px-6 py-2 md:py-3 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl text-[10px] md:text-xs font-black uppercase italic text-indigo-600 shadow-lg border border-indigo-100">One-Piece Collection</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-20 md:mt-32 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-4 text-slate-900">Need Custom OEM/ODM or Private Label?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-6">We offer full customization: fabric selection, color matching, logo embroidery/printing, custom packaging. MOQ from 10 sets/color.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-secondary text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-700 transition shadow-lg">Request Custom Quote →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Global Size Guide -->
    <div class="mt-20 md:mt-40 pt-12 md:pt-20 border-t border-slate-100">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 md:mb-8 text-center italic">Global Size Guide</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 md:mb-12 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto italic">Ensure the perfect fit for your team. Our scrubs are designed with a tailored fit ranging from XXS to 6XL.</p>
      
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-lg md:shadow-2xl">
        <table class="w-full text-left bg-white italic">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-primary text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
              <th class="p-3 md:p-6 text-xs md:text-sm">Size</th>
              <th class="p-6">Chest (cm)</th>
              <th class="p-6">Waist (cm)</th>
              <th class="p-6">Hip (cm)</th>
              <th class="p-6">US Size</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-slate-700">
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">XXS</td>
              <td class="p-6">88</td>
              <td class="p-6">78</td>
              <td class="p-6">92</td>
              <td class="p-6">0–2</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">XS</td>
              <td class="p-6">92</td>
              <td class="p-6">82</td>
              <td class="p-6">96</td>
              <td class="p-6">4–6</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">S</td>
              <td class="p-6">98</td>
              <td class="p-6">88</td>
              <td class="p-6">102</td>
              <td class="p-6">8–10</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">M</td>
              <td class="p-6">104</td>
              <td class="p-6">94</td>
              <td class="p-6">108</td>
              <td class="p-6">12–14</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">L</td>
              <td class="p-6">110</td>
              <td class="p-6">100</td>
              <td class="p-6">114</td>
              <td class="p-6">16–18</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">XL</td>
              <td class="p-6">116</td>
              <td class="p-6">106</td>
              <td class="p-6">120</td>
              <td class="p-6">20–22</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">2XL</td>
              <td class="p-6">122</td>
              <td class="p-6">112</td>
              <td class="p-6">126</td>
              <td class="p-6">24–26</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-100">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">3XL</td>
              <td class="p-6">128</td>
              <td class="p-6">118</td>
              <td class="p-6">132</td>
              <td class="p-6">28–30</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50">
              <td class="p-3 md:p-6 font-black text-primary text-xs md:text-sm">4XL–6XL</td>
              <td class="p-6" colspan="4">Available for most styles. Contact us for plus-size availability and MOQ.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center mt-6"><a href="/size-guide" class="text-secondary font-bold hover:underline">View Complete Size Guide →</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
